        public List<co.cask.cdap.proto.ScheduledRuntime> nextRuntimes(co.cask.cdap.proto.Id.Workflow workflow)
                                                       throws IOException,
                                                              co.cask.cdap.common.UnauthenticatedException,
                                                              co.cask.cdap.common.NotFoundException,
                                                              co.cask.cdap.security.spi.authorization.UnauthorizedException
        Get the next scheduled run time of the program. A program may contain multiple schedules. This method returns the next scheduled runtimes for all the schedules. This method only takes + into account Schedules based on time. For schedules based on data, an empty list will + be returned.
        Parameters:
        workflow - Id of the Workflow for which to fetch next run times.
        Returns:
        list of Scheduled runtimes for the Workflow. Empty list if there are no schedules.
        Throws:
        IOException
